frontmatter.projectAddress: Heritage Park, Al Mina, Abu Dhabi
frontmatter.featuredDescription: The verse: 'معكم ثقافه و علم و إتقان' from Sheikh Zayed’s poem, 'الشباب الباني' was the main inspiration behind the design of our pavilion. The design consists of three main concrete blocks. The large, 3 meter tall block imitates a book, representing knowledge and signifies Abu Dhabi Youth Hub as a center for the exchange of ideas.
